data.meta_description: Andrew Kooman is an award-winning writer and producer who writes for the page, stage and screen. His critically acclaimed work has been produced around the world and translated into more than 14 languages. His film She Has A Name explores the global corruption of Human trafficking in the dark world of Bangkok crime. http://andrewkooman.com/she-has-a-name
